'''海倫·索莫斯'''（{{lang-en|Helen Sommers}}；{{bd|1932年|3月29日|2017年|3月7日|catIdx=Sommers}}），是美國的[[民主黨_(美國)|民主黨]]政治人物，前{{le|華盛頓州眾議院|Washington House of Representatives}}議員。

==生平==
索莫斯生於[[新澤西州|新澤西州]][[伍德伯里_(新澤西州)|伍德伯里]]，曾在[[華盛頓大學|華盛頓大學]]就讀<ref>[http://apps.leg.wa.gov/oralhistory/sommers/ Helen Sommers: An Oral History] {{Wayback|url=http://apps.leg.wa.gov/oralhistory/sommers/ |date=20151019101228 }}, {{le|華盛頓州眾議院|Washington State Legislature|Washington State Legislature}}. Accessed November 4, 2015. "Helen Sommers grew up in Woodbury Heights, New Jersey, in the '30s."</ref>，也曾擔任[[哈佛大学|哈佛大学]]的查爾斯·布拉德森林研究員<ref name="google">{{cite book|title=Washington State Yearbook|author1=Washington (State). Office of the Governor|author2=Washington (State). Office of the Secretary of State|date=1999|publisher=Information Press|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=tXQnAQAAMAAJ|accessdate=2015-08-13|archive-date=2017-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171223215919/https://books.google.ca/books?id=tXQnAQAAMAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

自1972年起，她以民主黨黨籍當選為華盛頓州眾議院第三十六選區代表議員<ref name="wa">{{cite web|url=http://apps.leg.wa.gov/oralhistory/sommers/HelenSommersOralHistoryBook.pdf|date=16 February 2011|title=Helen Sommers – An Oral History – 1973-2009|publisher=Washington State Legislature Oral History Program|isbn=978-0-9827541-1-5|accessdate=2015-08-13|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125183055/https://apps.leg.wa.gov/oralhistory/sommers/HelenSommersOralHistoryBook.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>，至2009年退休，是當時{{le|華盛頓州議會|Washington State Legislature}}服務時期最長的議員<ref name="seattletimes">{{cite web|url=http://seattletimes.com/html/localnews/2004275718_websommers11m.html|title=State Rep. Helen Sommers to retire | The Seattle Times|publisher=seattletimes.com|accessdate=2015-08-13|archive-date=2014-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140108055637/http://seattletimes.com/html/localnews/2004275718_websommers11m.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2017年3月7日，索莫斯在[[佛羅里達州|佛羅里達州]][[棕櫚灘花園|棕櫚灘花園]]逝世，享年84歲<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.nwcn.com/news/politics/former-state-rep-helen-sommers-dies-at-84/420640095|title = Former State Rep. Helen Sommers dies at 84|last = Barnes|first = Shelby|website = {{le|西北有線新聞台|Northwest Cable News|Northwest Cable News}}|publisher = {{le|台格納|Tegna, Inc.|Tegna, Inc.}}|date = March 7, 2017|accessdate = March 7, 2017|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170308144616/http://www.nwcn.com/news/politics/former-state-rep-helen-sommers-dies-at-84/420640095|archivedate = 2017年3月8日}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.seattletimes.com/seattle-news/politics/rep-helen-sommers-dies-she-served-in-the-house-36-years/|title=Rep. Helen Sommers dies; she served in state House for 36 years|last=O'Sullivan|first=Joseph|website=[[西雅图时报|The Seattle Times]]|publisher=The Seattle Times Company|date=March 8, 2017|accessdate=March 8, 2017|archive-date=2020-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128072921/https://www.seattletimes.com/seattle-news/politics/rep-helen-sommers-dies-she-served-in-the-house-36-years/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

